    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把三个参与者按顺序排好：Clinical Engineer、Azure Backup Vault、Workload VM。第一条消息是临床工程师配置策略到Azure。",
      "elements_involved": [
